      "title": "What is النسبة?",
      "titleArabic": "تعريف النسبة",
      "content": [
        "النسبة is forming a relative adjective by adding يّ (shadda on ya) to a noun to show attribution or belonging.",
        "For example: مِصْر → مِصْرِيّ (Egyptian), إِسْلَام → إِسْلَامِيّ (Islamic)."
      ],
      "keyPoints": [
        "Add يّ to create attribution: مِصْر → مِصْرِيّ",
        "Feminine adds ـة: مِصْرِيَّة",
        "Used for nationalities, religions, affiliations",
        "Common examples: عَرَبِيّ، إِنْجِلِيزِيّ، إِسْلَامِيّ"
      ],
      "examples": [
        { "arabic": "هُوَ رَجُلٌ مِصْرِيٌّ", "english": "He is an Egyptian man" },
